{
  "texts": [
    "Words are treated as nodes in the graph representation.",
    "Next, the center words in each window were connected to the other words within the window.",
    "This step establishes connections between the center word and the surrounding words, capturing the local context and relationships within the neighborhood of the center word.",
    "Furthermore, to capture the long-distance dependency, they merged all occurrences of the same words into a single node in the graph.",
    "This consolidation explicitly gathers the local contexts of these word instances: if there is one claim and n evidences, the framework constructs (n + 1) graphs. 2."
  ]
}